OL,3,CScience museum We The Curious reopens
OL,4,Ctwo years after devastating fire
OL,6,FThe Bristol science museum We The
OL,7,FCurious has reopened for the first
OL,8,Ftime in more than two years after a
OL,9,Fdevastating fire forced it to shut.
OL,11,FSchool children from Cornwall were
OL,12,Famong the first to return to the site.
OL,13,FThey were cheered in by staff who said
OL,14,Fit was a 'hugely emotional and
OL,15,Fimportant' day.
OL,17,FThe fire in April 2022 started on
OL,18,Fsolar panels on the roof but led to
OL,19,Fsignificant water damage after gallons
OL,20,Fof water was pumped onto the building.
