OL,3,CScience museum We The Curious reopens
OL,4,Ctwo years after devastating fire
OL,6,FChief executive, Donna Speed described
OL,7,Fthe last two years as "bumpy and
OL,8,Fchallenging" but said it was
OL,9,F"incredible" to reopen.
OL,11,FShe said: "It feels fantastic to be
OL,12,Fback. We have been closed for two
OL,13,Fyears and two months and we've really
OL,14,Fmissed our visitors. To see people
OL,15,Fback here is incredible."
OL,17,FIt took six months for the building to
OL,18,Fbe fully dried out after the fire
OL,19,Fbefore repairs could be carried out
OL,20,Fincluding a new roof and solar panels.
