OL,3,CScience museum We The Curious reopens
OL,4,Ctwo years after devastating fire
OL,6,FThe fire was caused by birds dropping
OL,7,Frocks onto some of the solar panels
OL,8,Fwhich led to a malfunction. The
OL,9,Fvisitor attraction had only been open
OL,10,Ffor ten months following the pandemic
OL,11,Fwhen the fire struck.
OL,13,FDonna Speed said: "After covid, which
OL,14,Fwas challenging in itself, it was not
OL,15,Fthat much longer when we had the fire
OL,16,Fon the roof and all the water damage.
